	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You add the <em>attack</em> and <em>weaponry</em> schools of magic to your fire lord spell list. You gain two spells from these schools when you gain this feature, they don’t count toward the number of spells you know.</p><p>When you take the Attack action, you can forgo making one attack to allow a friendly creature within 15ft of you to make an attack instead. If the target can hear or see you, it can use its reaction to either cast a cantrip or make one weapon attack.</p>",
